{"tid":766291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女說自己學不會拒絕 男舔她胸部半小時挨告","createTime":"2018-08-03T13:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T14:25:51.000Z","uid":37554,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a18a2841ed107d95a98871081a39f12f19a86d73","tid":766291,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpqoXZdg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpqoXZdg.jpg&h=355a8fdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕今年4月，一名黃姓男子約女性好友看夜景，過程中男子舔她的胸部，女子過程中沒有拒絕，事後指控黃男強制性交，並稱自己沒拒絕不代表同意。台北地檢署處分黃男不起訴。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》報導，黃姓男子當天與女性好友在圓山飯店看夜景，之後開到中山北路停車格，男子對這美好夜晚意猶未竟，親吻、撫摸對方胸部、下體。報導指出，女子事後指控，黃男有問她想不想做，她還沒回應黃男就舔她胸部半小時。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，黃男稱自己當天並無違反對方意願，女子則說自己一直學不會拒絕，但不代表她同意。檢方認為，女子不會拒絕，黃男可能誤認對方意圖，無法認定他有強制性交犯意，處分不起訴。"},{"pid":"b3ee34aeccba32f48ec5526aa7b8e69def566632","tid":766291,"uid":102872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"所"},{"pid":"f15de94af7eccf9528ef243f80df5da699d18f6d","tid":766291,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:27:20.000Z","msg":"L,\\M"},{"pid":"d8951588dcd0cd65eebd63ef3be7314707e4615a","tid":766291,"uid":122709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:32:08.000Z","msg":"Goalllll"},{"pid":"066806cb9dbad688ed88716a3af1b83449f4d42a","tid":766291,"uid":41368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:40:08.000Z","msg":"未睇內文已經知又係台灣"},{"pid":"9baaf80e52352fbdde846bf1de6ed97eefd02de0","tid":766291,"uid":170229,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:03:19.000Z","msg":"學不會拒絕係條女自己嘅問題"},{"pid":"d7645bd3a5bffed4c838e99d4ab20639f5c25baa","tid":766291,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\"